Have I written custom code
1.Add call to SetUseNNAPI(true) inside ImageClassifier.java constructor
2.comment on ` url 'https://google.bintray.com/tensorflow' in tensorflow-master\tensorflow\contrib\lite\java\demo\app\build.gradle - It load old tensorflow lite library

OS Platform and Distribution
Ubuntu 17.10
TensorFlow installed from
Github
TensorFlow version
Master Clone 3 days ago
Bazel version
0.10.1
CUDA/cuDNN version
No VM VirtualBox Machine
GPU model and memory
No VM VirtualBox Machine
Exact command to reproduce

bazel build --cxxopt=--std=c++11 //tensorflow/contrib/lite/java/demo/app/src/main:TfLiteCameraDemo --config=android_arm64 --cpu=arm64-v8a --fat_apk_cpu=arm64-v8a
